    <briefdescription>
<para>USB Audio Class 2 device public header. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This header describes only class API interaction with application. The audio device itself is modelled with devicetree zephyr,uac2 compatible.</para>
<para>This API is currently considered experimental. </para>
